p: Thirty-seven volatile constituents, representing 98.8% of the total composition were identified in the twig oil, 12 of them exceeding 1%. The most abundant constituents found in the twig EO (above 3%) were 1,8-cineole (48.5%), α-terpinyl acetate (13.1%), methyl eugenol (6.6%), β-linalool (3.8%), β -pinene (3.4%), sabinene (3.3%), and terpinene-4-ol (3.3%).
